  "instructions": [
    "In a large bowl, combine arugula, roasted pepper, olives, fennel, and capers.",
    "Sprinkle smoked paprika, sea salt, and black pepper over the greens and toss gently.",
    "Add the diced Manchego cheese and toasted pine nuts, stirring to distribute evenly.",
    "Whisk olive oil and lemon juice in a small bowl until emulsified, then drizzle over the salad.",
    "Toss the salad again to coat all ingredients with the vinaigrette.",
    "Let the salad rest for 2 minutes to allow flavors to meld.",
    "Sprinkle extra smoked paprika on top for an intense smoky hint.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with a few fresh parsley leaves if desired."
